            </li>
            <li><strong>CloudWatch:</strong> Monitoring and logging</li>
            <li><strong>VPC:</strong> Virtual Private Cloud, subnets, security groups</li>
            <li><strong>IAM:</strong> Identity and Access Management, roles, policies</li>
        </ul>

